description:
This is the additional puzzle pack for "Jigsaw Masterpieces". The following 10 puzzle images are included.
-Canal of Murano Island, Venice
-View from the Tiber to St. Peter's Basilica
-Mortorio Island
-Bolzano and the Dolomites
-Main Village of Vernazza
-Budelli
-Port of Scilla
-Lake Como
-Sardinia
-Polignano a Mare in the evening
name: Italy - Most beautiful places in the World -
